headline: Is Intercontinental Exchange Worth a Fresh Look After $2B Polymarket Investment Talks?
summary: If you are eyeing Intercontinental Exchange (ICE) right now, you are likely wondering whether the recent price swings signal a real opportunity or just more market noise. After a rocky patch, with shares down nearly 11% over the last month and off 6.9% since this time last year, some investors are questioning if now is the moment to buy, hold, or just wait and see.
